  <name>LXI-Tools</name>
  <summary>
    LXI-Tools is a collection of open source tools for managing LXI compatible
    test instruments.
  </summary>
  <description>
    <p>
      The lxi tool is a commandline program that supports various operations to
      manage your LXI compatible test instrument on your network, including:
      discovery, sending SCPI commands, downloading screenshots, benchmarking,
      scripting.
    </p>
    <p>
      The lxi-gui tool is a GUI application which supports operations similar to
      that of the lxi commandline tool.
    </p>
  </description>
